desc_en: Situated 5 km from Ibn Battuta Mall in Dubai, this apartment features a garden with an outdoor pool. The property is 7 km from Mall of the Emirates and free private parking is available. Free WiFi is featured throughout the property.

name: La Villa Eilat
desc_en: La Villa Eilat is located 1 km from the centre of Eilat. It offers air-conditioned accommodation with free Wi-Fi access and a furnished patio.  The accommodation will provide you with a flat-screen satellite TV and a refrigerator.

name: Nawara Mohamdia Branch
address: Intersection of Imam Saoud and Takhasosi Str.
desc_en: Nawara Mohamdia Branch is located in Riyadh, about 3 km from Northern Ring Road. Gallery Mall is 20 minutes away by car. Wi-Fi is available free of charge.  The apartments are air conditioned and feature a seating area with a sofa and flat-screen TV.
